== {{<a id="research"></a>}}Research interests

- [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematical_optimization Mathematical optimization] and its applications, especially
-- [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Derivative-free_optimization derivative-free] (zeroth-order) methods
-- randomized methods
-- methods for large-scale problems
-- methods for noisy problems

